| **Input Validation** | Validate and sanitize all inputs |
| **Error Handling** | Never expose stack traces to clients |
| **Security Headers** | Use `helmet` for HTTP headers |
| **Payload Limits** | Restrict JSON/URL-encoded body size |
| **Logging** | Log all requests and errors |
| **Environment Variables** | Never hard-code sensitive values |
| **Error Recovery** | Handle uncaught exceptions gracefully |

